Make symlinks for the lib-folder and the folders for 
https://github.com/Kagee/scraperwiki-python
and
https://github.com/Kagee/dumptruck
in "python -m site --user-site" to use these scripts

In addition you will probably need the following (debian 7.4) packages:
python-beautifulsoup python-lxml python-cssselect 
python-virtualenv python-pip python-sqlite sqlite3 
python-pdftools python-dateutil python-bs4 
python-mechanize python-yaml poppler-utils 
python-psycopg2 python-requests
